<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, December 2 (Xinhua) -- Turkish President Suleyman
Demirel on Wednesday assigned Democratic Left Party leader and
Deputy Prime Minister Bulent Ecevit to form a new government.
</P>
<P>
Ecevit made the announcement after meeting with Demirel at
