<HEADLINE> Trott Moloto Named Coach of South Africa </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, December 3 (Xinhua) -- Trott Moloto signed a
contract with South Africa as their national coach until March
2000 on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Moloto, 42, was the caretaker coach when South Africa took
part in the African Nations' Cup in October.
</P>
<P>
Moloto was assistant coach to Frenchman Philippe Troussier at
the World Cup in France this summer. 
</P>
