<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, December 3 (Xinhua) -- Share prices on the Kuala
Lumpur Stock Exchange closed mixed Thursday.
</P>
<P>
At the close, the 100-quality stocks Composite Index fell 4.99
points to 521.76, the all-share Emas Index lost 0.23 of a point to
142.29 and the Industrial Index lost 10.97 points to 1,008.68.
</P>
<P>
