concerts and operas, including the classic "Turandot."
</P>
<P>
The city has established a special art fund so that the hall's
presentations can be made financially accessible to the general
public.
</P>
<P>
The first performance will be a New Year's concert by the Hong
Kong Chinese Orchestra as a salute to those Hong Kong and Macao
compatriots who donated to the building of the memorial hall,
sources said.  
