<HEADLINE> Webber Avoids Jail Sentence on Court </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, December 2 (Xinhua) -- NBA Sacramento Kings
forward Chris Webber survived from a jail sentence when he was
cleared today of the most serious charges on the court in
Maryland.
