<HEADLINE> White House Lawyers to Defend Clinton Against Impeachment </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, December 2 (Xinhua) -- The White House on Wednesday
accepted an invitation to appear before the Judiciary Committee of
the U.S. House of Representatives to defend President Bill Clinton
against impeachment charges.
